| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3359 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4fd7d606-9d2e-5db3-b23f-3e86e19142e9"
